OL,3,CFirst UK couple to be married on the
OL,4,CChannel Islands' sole railway line
OL,6,FA UK couple has become the first man
OL,7,Fand woman to be married on a train in .
OL,9,FPaul and Katie are from the Lake
OL,10,FDistrict and tied the knot on Thursday
OL,11,F30 May while riding the Alderney Train.
OL,13,FIn 2021, the island changed its
OL,14,Fmarriage laws as they were considered
OL,15,Foutdated and did not meet the
OL,16,Frequirements of modern society.
OL,18,FThe changes simplified the process and
OL,19,Fallowed weddings in almost any
OL,20,Flocation, including the island's
OL,21,Fbeaches and hotels.
