OL,4,CChannel Islands' sole railway line
OL,6,FThe couple picked Alderney for their
OL,7,Fwedding destination as Katie had
OL,8,Fregularly visited on holiday as a
OL,9,Fchild.
OL,11,FAfter revisiting with Paul, the two
OL,12,Fdecided they wanted to do something
OL,13,Funconventional for their special day.
OL,15,FThe guests arrived at Alderney's
OL,16,Frailway station around lunchtime.
OL,18,FAfter the ceremony, the newlyweds and
OL,19,Fguests travelled on the train to
OL,20,FQuarry, before returning to the Braye
OL,21,FBeach Hotel for the reception.
