OL,6,FKatie said: "We never wanted to be
OL,7,Fvery traditional when we got married
OL,8,Fso it just seemed like the perfect
OL,9,Flocation."
OL,11,FPaul said having the wedding in
OL,12,FAlderney was "absolutely brilliant."
OL,14,FCivil Celebrant Annabell Finding was
OL,15,Fthe wedding officiant; she hopes the
OL,16,Ffreedom given by the new marriage laws
OL,17,Fwill attract more visitors to the
OL,18,Fisland.
